jeremyText="After some time, these become invulnerable to taking damage, but you know what to do there. Something different for them though, they try to stay attached to the body, so you'll need to be very close to get Kirby to eat them. Oh yes, when you see a charging up like particle effect on the body segments, it's about to fire a laser." chaoText="These don't give any ability when eaten, but they do restore 1/2 of a heart... wow that's pretty bad." devText="N/A"
